#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "&keurocalc; is an universal pocket currency converter and calculator."
msgstr "&keurocalc; je univerzalni žepni pretvornik valut in kalkulator."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the 1st of January, 2002, 12 European countries united their national "
"currencies into a single one, the euro (€). The same happens from time to "
"time on a smaller scale with new European countries. &keurocalc; helps:"
msgstr ""
"1. januarja 2002 je 12 evropskih držav svoje nacionalne valute združilo v "
"eno samo evro (€). Enako se občasno zgodi v manjšem obsegu z novimi "
"evropskimi državami. &keurocalc; pomaga:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "During the transition periods"
msgstr "V prehodnih obdobjih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To verify one's bank account, when paying both in euros and in the old "
"currency (Italian liras, for example)."
msgstr ""
"Za preverjanje bančnega računa pri plačilu tako v evrih kot v stari valuti "
"(na primer italijanskih lirah)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To verify one's shopping, and compute the change if paying with a banknote "
"labeled in the old currency."
msgstr ""
"Za preverjanje nakupovanja in izračun drobiža pri plačilu z bankovcem, "
"označenim v stari valuti."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many years after the transition periods"
msgstr "Mnogo let po prehodnih obdobjih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get an idea of the value of the things in the old currency at any stage "
"of calculations."
msgstr ""
"Dobiti predstavo o vrednosti stvari v stari valuti na kateri koli stopnji "
"izračuna."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "At any time"
msgstr "Kadarkoli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between the euro and other currencies, like the British "
"Pound, according to the daily exchange rate published by the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/eurofxref/\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za pretvorbe med evrom in drugimi valutami, kot je britanski funt, v skladu "
"z dnevnim menjalnim tečajem, ki ga objavlja <ulink url=\"http://www.ecb.int/"
"stats/eurofxref/\">Evropska centralna banka (ECB) )</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between any two currencies that are part of the list "
"published by the ECB."
msgstr ""
"Za pretvorbe med katerima koli dvema valutama, ki sta del seznama, ki ga je "
"objavila ECB."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between the euro and other currencies, like the British "
"Pound, according to the daily exchange rate published by the <ulink url="
"\"http://rss.timegenie.com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie</ulink> "
"foreign exchange (TG)."
msgstr ""
"Za pretvorbe med evrom in drugimi valutami, kot je britanski funt, v skladu "
"z dnevnim menjalnim tečajem, ki ga objavlja menjalnica <ulink url=\"http://"
"rss.timegenie.com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie</ulink> (TG)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between any two currencies that are part of the list "
"published by the TG."
msgstr ""
"Za pretvorbe med katerima koli dvema valutama, ki sta del seznama, ki ga je "
"objavila TG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&keurocalc; has the following advantages in term of comfort and usability:"
msgstr "&keurocalc; ima naslednje prednosti v smislu udobja in uporabnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You see every intermediate value and the result in both the reference "
"currency (euro) and in the other currency."
msgstr ""
"Vsako vmesno vrednost in rezultat vidite v referenčni valuti (evro) in v "
"drugi valuti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a separate input area where you can type a new value while still "
"having the previous result visible."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja ločeno vnosno območje, kjer lahko vnesete novo vrednost, medtem ko "
"je prejšnji rezultat še vedno viden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ergonomy is very close to usual pocket calculators, despite the fact "
"that any value you type can be a value in the reference currency (euro), a "
"value in the other currency, a percentage or an unit-less quantity."
msgstr ""
"Ergonomija je zelo blizu običajnim žepnim kalkulatorjem, kljub temu, da je "
"lahko katera koli vrednost, ki jo vtipkate, vrednost v referenčni valuti "
"(evro), vrednost v drugi valuti, odstotek ali količina brez enote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You press the keys in the order you would speak aloud what you're doing."
msgstr "Tipke pritiskate v vrstnem redu, kot bi na glas govorili, kaj počnete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you make mistakes, a special correction button enables you to correct "
"your last input data, as long as you didn't validate."
msgstr ""
"Če se zmotite, vam poseben gumb za popravek omogoča, da popravite zadnje "
"vnesene podatke, v kolikor niste validirali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numbers are displayed according to your locale settings: with either a "
"comma or a dot as a decimal point, according to your &systemsettings; "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Številke so prikazane glede na vaše lokalne nastavitve: z vejico ali piko "
"kot decimalno vejico, glede na vaše nastavitve &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decide where &keurocalc; should download the conversion rates from, "
"which currency to start with when you launch &keurocalc;, and which rounding "
"method to use."
msgstr ""
"Sami se lahko odločite, kje bo &keurocalc; prenesti menjalne tečaje, s "
"katero valuto začeti, ko zaženete &keurocalc;, in kateri način zaokroževanja "
"uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "&keurocalc; allows the following operations:"
msgstr "&keurocalc; omogoča naslednje operacije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conversions from and to the reference currency (euro)."
msgstr "Pretvorbe iz in v referenčno valuto (evro)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Systematic rounding of the displayed result, but computations done "
"internally with the precision of the mathematical libraries."
msgstr ""
"Sistematično zaokroževanje prikazanega rezultata, vendar izračuni izvedeni "
"interno z natančnostjo matematičnih knjižnic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usual additions, subtractions, multiplications and divisions."
msgstr "Običajno seštevanje, odštevanje, množenje in deljenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply a percentage, add a percentage, or subtract a percentage."
msgstr "Uporabite odstotek, dodajte odstotek ali odštejte odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Possibility to store values in an intermediate memory, or use that memory as "
"a running total."
msgstr ""
"Možnost shranjevanja vrednosti v vmesnem pomnilniku ali uporabe tega "
"pomnilnika kot tekoče vsote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some limitations of &keurocalc;:"
msgstr "Tukaj je nekaj omejitev &keurocalc;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "No parenthesized or complex expressions."
msgstr "Brez oklepajev ali zapletenih izrazov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some roundings go wrong due to the limitations of the mathematical library."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera zaokroževanja gredo narobe zaradi omejitev matematične knjižnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inflationist currencies cannot be handled due to limited display size. "
"However, with the change to the new Turkish lira and the removal of six "
"zeroes in that currency, it is not a practical problem anymore."
msgstr ""
"Inflacijskih valut ni mogoče obravnavati zaradi omejene velikosti zaslona. "
"Vendar s spremembo v novo turško liro in odstranitvijo šestih ničel v tej "
"valuti to ni več praktičen problem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&keurocalc; never guarantees the exactness of the exchange rates nor the "
"accuracy of the result. You are always invited to verify your computations "
"by some other means. As the <link linkend=\"credits\">license</link> "
"agreement states, there's no liability of the authors if the results are not "
"correct or as expected. Also, please notice that the variable exchange rates "
"are downloaded in an unencrypted and therefore insecure manner from the data "
"sources (European Central Bank and Time Genie). Some <quote>man-in-the-"
"middle</quote> attacker may confuse &keurocalc; by forging exchange rates. "
"More simply, a transmission error is always possible."
msgstr ""
"&keurocalc; nikoli ne jamči za točnost menjalnih tečajev niti za točnost "
"rezultata. Vedno ste vabljeni, da preverite svoje izračune na kak drug "
"način. Kot je navedeno v <link linkend=\"credits\">licenčni</link> pogodbi, "
"avtorji ne prevzemajo nobene odgovornosti, če rezultati niso pravilni ali "
"pričakovani. Upoštevajte tudi, da so spremenljivi menjalni tečaji preneseni "
"na nešifriran in zato nevaren način iz virov podatkov (Evropska centralna "
"banka in Time Genie). Nekateri napadalci <quote>man-in-the-middle</quote> "
"lahko zmedejo &keurocalc; s kovanjem menjalnih tečajev. Preprosteje, napaka "
"pri prenosu je vedno možna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &keurocalc;"
msgstr "Uporaba &keurocalc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Performing Conversions"
msgstr "Izvajanje pretvorb"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 1000 Belgian francs into euros"
msgstr "Za pretvorbo 1000 belgijskih frankov v evre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>BEF - Belgian franc</guilabel> (<foreignphrase>francs "
"belges</foreignphrase>) item in the currencies drop down list on the bottom. "
"If that choice is not available, press the <guibutton>Settings...</"
"guibutton> button and select <guilabel>Euro, no network access (fixed rates "
"only)</guilabel> to make the correct rates list appear."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu valut na dnu izberite element <guilabel>BEF - belgijski "
"frank</guilabel> (<foreignphrase>francs belges</foreignphrase>). Če ta "
"možnost ni na voljo, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nastavitve...</guibutton> in "
"izberite <guilabel>Evro, brez dostopa do omrežja (samo fiksne tarife)</"
"guilabel>, da se prikaže seznam pravilnih cen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>1000</userinput> on the keyboard or use the corresponding "
"numerical buttons. The digits appear while you are typing them in the "
"<guilabel>Input</guilabel> display. If you make a mistake while typing the "
"digits use the &Backspace; key or the <guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Vtipkajte <userinput>1000</userinput> na tipkovnici ali uporabite ustrezne "
"številske gumbe. Številke se prikažejo, medtem ko jih tipkate na zaslonu "
"<guilabel>Vnos</guilabel>. Če se med vnašanjem številk zmotite, uporabite "
"&Backspace; tipko ali gumb <guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>FB</guibutton> button or the <keycap>F</keycap> key. In "
"fact, any key that is not already reserved for some other usage will "
"validate the input as a number expressed in the currency, so <keycap>B</"
"keycap> or <keycap>X</keycap> would have worked as well."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>FB</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>F</keycap>. "
"Pravzaprav bo vsak ključ, ki še ni rezerviran za kakšno drugo uporabo, "
"potrdil vnos kot število, izraženo v valuti, zato bi tudi <keycap>B</keycap> "
"ali <keycap>X</keycap> delovala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right: "
"24.79 € or 24,79 € according to our locale settings."
msgstr ""
"Preberite rezultat v prikazu <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> na desni: 24,79 € "
"ali 24,79 € glede na naše lokalne nastavitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 25 euros into Belgian francs"
msgstr "Za pretvorbo 25 evrov v belgijske franke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the fixed rates currencies are available, select the <guilabel>BEF - "
"Belgian franc</guilabel> item in the currencies drop down list on the "
"bottom. You can skip this step if it's already the selected currency."
msgstr ""
"Če so na voljo valute s fiksnim tečajem, izberite element <guilabel>BEF - "
"belgijski frank</guilabel> na spustnem seznamu valut na dnu. Ta korak lahko "
"preskočite, če je že izbrana valuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>25</userinput>."
msgstr "Vnesite <userinput>25</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>€</guibutton> button or the <keycap>E</keycap> key."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>€</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>E</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right: "
"1008.50 FB or 1008,50 FB. The exact value is 1008.4975, but it's rounded to "
"the closest hundredth of a Belgian franc. The rounding unit depends on the "
"currency and on the rounding method: with the official rounding rules, for "
"Belgian francs it's 0.01 FB, for Italian liras it's 1 L for example."
msgstr ""
"Preberite rezultat v prikazu <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> na desni: 1008,50 "
"FB ali 1008,50 FB. Natančna vrednost je 1008,4975, vendar je zaokrožena na "
"najbližjo stotinko belgijskega franka. Enota zaokroževanja je odvisna od "
"valute in načina zaokroževanja: z uradnimi pravili zaokroževanja je za "
"belgijske franke 0,01 FB, za italijanske lire je na primer 1 L."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "You could also have typed: <userinput>25 Enter E</userinput>."
msgstr "Lahko bi tudi vnesli: <userinput>25 Enter E</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 120 German marks into Spanish pesetas"
msgstr "Če želite pretvoriti 120 nemških mark v španske pezete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the fixed rates currencies are available, select the <guilabel>DEM - "
"German deutschmark</guilabel> item in the currencies drop down list."
msgstr ""
"Če so na voljo valute s fiksnim tečajem, na spustnem seznamu valut izberite "
"element <guilabel>DEM - nemške nemške marke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>120</userinput>."
msgstr "Vnesite <userinput>120</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>DM</guibutton> button or the <keycap>D</keycap> or "
"<keycap>M</keycap> keys."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>DM</guibutton> ali tipki <keycap>D</keycap> ali "
"<keycap>M</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just select the <guilabel>ESP - Spanish peseta</guilabel> item to see the "
"same amount of 61.36 € converted into pesetas in the <guilabel>Result</"
"guilabel> area."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto izberite element <guilabel>ESP - španska pezeta</guilabel>, da "
"vidite isti znesek 61,36 €, pretvorjen v pezete v območju "
"<guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding and Subtracting"
msgstr "Seštevanje in odštevanje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3 + 5?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3 + 5?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>3</userinput> and then press <guibutton>+</guibutton>. "
"Notice that in the result field, <computeroutput>3</computeroutput> is a "
"simple value displayed on just one line, with no monetary unit."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>3</userinput> in pritisnite <guibutton>+</guibutton>. "
"Upoštevajte, da je v polju z rezultati <computeroutput>3</computeroutput> "
"preprosta vrednost, prikazana v samo eni vrstici, brez denarne enote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>5</userinput> and then press the <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> button or the &Enter; key. The result <computeroutput>8</"
"computeroutput> appears on the right."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>5</userinput> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> ali gumb &Enter;. Rezultat <computeroutput>8</computeroutput> se "
"prikaže na desni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You received 100 US dollars and paid 32.50 euros for a book, how much do you "
"have left in your bank account?"
msgstr ""
"Za knjigo ste prejeli 100 ameriških dolarjev in plačali 32,50 evra, koliko "
"vam je ostalo na bančnem računu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that the variable exchange rates are available. If not, press the "
"<guibutton>Settings...</guibutton> to select either <guilabel>Euro, European "
"Central Bank</guilabel> or <guilabel>Euro, Time Genie</guilabel>. Now select "
"the <guilabel>USD - US dollar</guilabel> item in the scroll down list on the "
"bottom. If you have no Internet access, that item won't be available as the "
"latest variable rates between the euro and the dollar cannot be determined."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so na voljo spremenljivi menjalni tečaji. Če ne, "
"pritisnite <guibutton>Nastavitve...</guibutton>, da izberete <guilabel>Evro, "
"Evropska centralna banka</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Evro, Time Genie</"
"guilabel>. Sedaj izberite element <guilabel>USD - ameriški dolar</guilabel> "
"na seznamu za drsenje navzdol na dnu. Če nimate dostopa do interneta, ta "
"element ne bo na voljo, ker ni mogoče določiti najnovejših spremenljivih "
"tečajev med evrom in dolarjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>100</userinput> and then press <guibutton>$</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>100</userinput> in pritisnite <guibutton>$</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or the <keycap>-</keycap> key. "
"Notice the <computeroutput>-</computeroutput> sign in the leftmost part of "
"the <guilabel>Input</guilabel> display."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>-</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>-</keycap>. "
"Opazite znak <computeroutput>-</computeroutput> v skrajnem levem delu "
"zaslona <guilabel>Vhod</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>32,50</userinput> or <userinput>32.50</userinput> and then "
"press <guibutton>€</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>32,50</userinput> ali <userinput>32,50</userinput> in "
"pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right. The "
"exact value might depend on latest exchange rates. Notice that during the "
"whole computation you've been able to read the values both in euro and in US "
"dollars. Pay attention to the fact that different data sources (ECB or TG) "
"might not provide the same conversion rate between the euro and the dollar."
msgstr ""
"Preberite rezultat v prikazu <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> na desni. "
"Natančna vrednost je lahko odvisna od zadnjih menjalnih tečajev. "
"Upoštevajte, da ste med celotnim izračunom lahko prebrali vrednosti tako v "
"evrih kot v ameriških dolarjih. Bodite pozorni na dejstvo, da različni viri "
"podatkov (ECB ali TG) morda ne zagotavljajo enakega menjalnega razmerja med "
"evrom in dolarjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You pay a 32.50 € book with a 500 FF banknote. How much was the clerk "
"supposed to give you back, in euro notes and coins?"
msgstr ""
"Knjigo za 32,50 € plačate z bankovcem za 500 FF. Koliko naj bi vam "
"uslužbenec vrnil v evrskih bankovcih in kovancih?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>FRF - French francs</guilabel> item in the currencies "
"drop down list if not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu valut izberite element <guilabel>FRF - francoski franki</"
"guilabel>, če še ni izbran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>32.50</userinput> or <userinput>32,50</userinput> and then "
"press <guibutton>€</guibutton>. You can also type <userinput>32.5</"
"userinput> without the trailing <userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>32,50</userinput> ali <userinput>32,50</userinput> in "
"pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>. Vnesete lahko tudi <userinput>32.5</"
"userinput> brez <userinput>0</userinput> na koncu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or the <keycap>-</keycap> key."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>-</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>-</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>500</userinput> and press the <guibutton>FF</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>F</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>500</userinput> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>FF</"
"guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>F</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result <computeroutput>-43.72 €</computeroutput> is negative, indicating "
"that change money has to be given back to the customer. The <guibutton>+/-</"
"guibutton> button or the <keycap>S</keycap> key permit you to change the "
"sign of the result."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat <computeroutput>-43,72 €</computeroutput> je negativen, kar pomeni, "
"da je treba denar vrniti stranki. Gumb <guibutton>+/-</guibutton> ali tipka "
"<keycap>S</keycap> vam omogočata, da spremenite predznak rezultata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not try to add euros to simple values (with no currency unit): it won't "
"work, for the same reason you cannot add 5 meters to 3 kilograms."
msgstr ""
"Evre ne poskušajte dodati preprostim vrednostim (brez denarne enote): ne bo "
"delovalo, iz istega razloga, kot ne morete dodati 5 metrov 3 kilogramom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiplying and Dividing"
msgstr "Množenje in deljenje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You buy 3.2 kilograms of apples at 2 € per kilogram. How much does the whole "
"cost in Australian dollars?"
msgstr ""
"Kupite 3,2 kilograma jabolk po 2 € za kilogram. Koliko stane celota v "
"avstralskih dolarjih?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>AUD - Australian dollar</guilabel> item if available "
"and if not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element <guilabel>AUD - avstralski dolar</guilabel>, če je na voljo "
"in če še ni izbran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>2</userinput> and press <guibutton>€</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>2</userinput> in pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>X</guibutton> button or the <keycap>*</keycap> key. "
"Notice the <computeroutput>X</computeroutput> sign at the left of the "
"<guilabel>Input</guilabel> display."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>X</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>*</keycap>. "
"Opazite znak <computeroutput>X</computeroutput> na levi strani zaslona "
"<guilabel>Vnos</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now type <userinput>3.2</userinput> followed by the <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> button or the &Enter; key: this means <quote>3.2 units</quote> at "
"2 € each."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj vnesite <userinput>3.2</userinput>, ki mu sledi gumb <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> ali tipka &Enter;: to pomeni <quote>3,2 enote</quote> po 2 € "
"vsaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result in Australian dollars matches <computeroutput>6.4 €</"
"computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat v avstralskih dolarjih se ujema s <computeroutput>6,4 €</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could also have used the following order: <userinput>3.2 = * 2 €</"
"userinput> or even <userinput>3.2 * 2 €</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Lahko bi uporabili tudi naslednji vrstni red: <userinput>3,2 = * 2 €</"
"userinput> ali celo <userinput>3,2 * 2 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's not possible to multiply X euros by Y dollars, just as you don't "
"multiply 10 fingers by 2 ears."
msgstr ""
"Ni mogoče pomnožiti X evrov z Y dolarji, tako kot ne pomnožite 10 prstov z 2 "
"ušesoma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Percentages"
msgstr "Uporaba odstotkov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 20% of 3000 yen?"
msgstr "Koliko je 20% od 3000 jenov?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334 index.docbook:346 index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>JPY - Japanese yen</guilabel> item if available and if "
"not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element <guilabel>JPY - japonski jen</guilabel>, če je na voljo in "
"če še ni izbran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336 index.docbook:348 index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>3000</userinput> and press the <guibutton>¥</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>Y</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>3000</userinput> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>¥</"
"guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>Y</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338 index.docbook:351 index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter <userinput>20</userinput> and press the <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>%</keycap> key. As with multiplications, the value had "
"to be typed <emphasis>before</emphasis> the percentage."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite <userinput>20</userinput> in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>%</"
"guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>%</keycap>. Tako kot pri množenju je bilo treba "
"vrednost vnesti <emphasis>pred</emphasis> odstotkom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look at the result: it is equivalent to 600 yen."
msgstr "Poglejte rezultat: enakovreden je 600 jenom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3000 yen plus 20%?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3000 jenov plus 20 %?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>+</guibutton> button or the <keycap>+</keycap> key."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>+</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>+</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look at the result: 26.96 € or 3600 ¥ at the time of writing."
msgstr "Poglejte rezultat: 26,96 € ali 3600 ¥ v času pisanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3000 yen minus 20%?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3000 jenov minus 20 %?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or <keycap>-</keycap> key."
msgstr "Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>-</guibutton> ali tipko <keycap>-</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look at the result: 17.97 € or 2400 ¥ at the date of writing these lines."
msgstr "Poglejte rezultat: 17,97 € oziroma 2400 ¥ na dan pisanja teh vrstic."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Intermediate Memory"
msgstr "Uporaba vmesnega pomnilnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I store now and recall later some value?"
msgstr "Kako zdaj shranim neko vrednost in jo pozneje prikličem?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do your computations."
msgstr "Naredite svoje izračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <guibutton>Min</guibutton> (Memory in) button to store the value in "
"the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> area. Please notice that the other memory "
"keys now become available."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Min</guibutton> (Memory in), da shranite vrednost "
"v območje <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da so drugi "
"pomnilniški ključi zdaj na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do some other work with the calculator."
msgstr "Naredite še kakšno delo s kalkulatorjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recall the value from the memory by pressing the <guibutton>MR</guibutton> "
"(Memory Recall) button."
msgstr ""
"Prikliči vrednost iz pomnilnika s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>MR</"
"guibutton> (Priklic pomnilnika)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Internally, the values are recalled with no unit or in the reference "
"currency (euro) with the maximum precision allowed by the mathematical "
"library. In some rare cases, this might lead to rounding problems if the "
"stored value is a rounded value in a non-reference currency."
msgstr ""
"Interno se vrednosti prikličejo brez enot ali v referenčni valuti (evro) z "
"največjo natančnostjo, ki jo dovoljuje matematična knjižnica. V nekaterih "
"redkih primerih lahko to povzroči težave z zaokroževanjem, če je shranjena "
"vrednost zaokrožena vrednost v nereferenčni valuti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I clear the memory?"
msgstr "Kako počistim pomnilnik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button. Please notice that the "
"<guibutton>Reset</guibutton> clears everything: the input, the result and "
"the memory."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton>. Upoštevajte, da "
"<guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton> počisti vse: vnos, rezultat in pomnilnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I compute 3.1 * 5.2 € + 2.7 * 8.9 €?"
msgstr "Kako izračunam 3,1 * 5,2 € + 2,7 * 8,9 €?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403 index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "First compute the first half: <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 €</userinput>."
msgstr "Najprej izračunajte prvo polovico: <userinput>3,1 * 5,2 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404 index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Store the result in memory with <guibutton>Min</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Shranite rezultat v pomnilnik z gumbom <guibutton>Min</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405 index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now compute the other half: <userinput>2.7 * 8.9 €</userinput>."
msgstr "Zdaj izračunajte drugo polovico: <userinput>2,7 * 8,9 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add the result to the memory with <guibutton>M+</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Dodajte rezultat v pomnilnik z gumbom <guibutton>M+</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407 index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recall the sum with <guibutton>MR</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Prikliči vsoto z gumbom <guibutton>MR</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are other solutions like <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € + MR</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo tudi druge rešitve, kot je <userinput>3,1 * 5,2 € Min. 2,7 * 8,9 € "
"+ MR</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I compute 3.1 * 5.2 € - 2.7 * 8.9 €?"
msgstr "Kako izračunam 3,1 * 5,2 € - 2,7 * 8,9 €?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Subtract the result from the memory with <guibutton>M-</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Odštejte rezultat iz pomnilnika z gumbom <guibutton>M-</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequence <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € - MR</userinput> "
"computes the difference in the reverse order."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedje <userinput>3,1 * 5,2 € Min 2,7 * 8,9 € - MR</userinput> izračuna "
"razliko v obratnem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Shortcuts"
msgstr "Privzete bližnjice"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt; <keycap>F4</keycap>"
msgstr "&Alt; <keycap>F4</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits from &keurocalc;"
msgstr "Izhod iz &keurocalc;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>0</keycap> - <keycap>9</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>0</keycap> - <keycap>9</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:449 index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Input digits"
msgstr "Vnesite številke"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>.</keycap> or <keycap>,</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>.</keycap> ali <keycap>,</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:452 index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decimal separator"
msgstr "Decimalno ločilo"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>+</keycap>, <keycap>-</keycap>, <keycap>*</keycap> and <keycap>/</"
"keycap>"
msgstr ""
"<keycap>+</keycap>, <keycap>-</keycap>, <keycap>*</keycap> in <keycap>/</"
"keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:455 index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operators: addition, subtraction, multiplication and division"
msgstr "Operatorji: seštevanje, odštevanje, množenje in deljenje"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Enter; and <keycap>Return</keycap>"
msgstr "&Enter; in <keycap>Vrni se</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:458 index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validation of input number considered as a simple, unitless, value"
msgstr ""
"Validacija vnesenega števila, obravnavanega kot preprosta vrednost brez enote"

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>%</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>%</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:461 index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validation of input number considered as a percentage"
msgstr "Validacija vnesene številke se šteje kot odstotek"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Backspace;"
msgstr "&Backspace;"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:464 index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removal of last input: digits, decimal separator or operator"
msgstr "Odstranitev zadnjega vnosa: števke, decimalno ločilo ali operator"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Tab; and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; &Tab;</keycombo> keys"
msgstr "&Tab; in <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; &Tab;</keycombo>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves from one button to the next or previous one"
msgstr "Premik z enega gumba na naslednjega ali prejšnjega"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow keys"
msgstr "Smerne tipke"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the currency selection area, moves from one currency to the other"
msgstr "V območju za izbiro valute se premika iz ene valute v drugo"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Space bar"
msgstr "Preslednica"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "When focus is on a push button, presses this button"
msgstr "Ko je fokus na gumbu, pritisne ta gumb"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>E</keycap> or <keycap>$</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>E</keycap> ali <keycap>$</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:476 index.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Validation of input number considered as a value expressed in the reference "
"currency (euro)"
msgstr ""
"Validacija vnesene številke, ki se šteje kot vrednost, izražena v referenčni "
"valuti (evrih)"

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>S</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>S</keycap>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:480 index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change sign of the result"
msgstr "Spremenite predznak rezultata"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any other key"
msgstr "Katera koli druga tipka"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:483 index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Validation of input number considered as a number in the other currency"
msgstr ""
"Potrditev vnesene številke, ki se obravnava kot številka v drugi valuti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "The buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>0</guibutton> to <guibutton>9</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>0</guibutton> do <guibutton>9</guibutton>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>.</guibutton> or <guibutton>,</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>.</guibutton> ali <guibutton>,</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;-"
msgstr "&lt;-"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>AC</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>AC</guibutton>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear all: both input and result area"
msgstr "Počisti vse: območje vnosa in rezultatov"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>€</guibutton> or <guibutton>$</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>€</guibutton> ali <guibutton>$</guibutton>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "The button labeled with the name of an other currency"
msgstr "Gumb, označen z imenom druge valute"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter"
msgstr "Vnesite"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>%</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>%</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>+/-</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>+/-</guibutton>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Min</guibutton>, <guibutton>MR</guibutton>, <guibutton>M+</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>-</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Min</guibutton>, <guibutton>MR</guibutton>, <guibutton>M+</"
"guibutton> in <guibutton>-</guibutton>"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Store result in memory, recall memory into result, add result to memory and "
"subtract result from memory"
msgstr ""
"Shrani rezultat v pomnilnik, prikliči pomnilnik v rezultat, dodaj rezultat v "
"pomnilnik in odštej rezultat od pomnilnika"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>/</guibutton>, <guibutton>X</guibutton>, <guibutton>-</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>+</guibutton>"
