msgstr "Prikaže polje <guilabel>Vizitka</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays these help pages"
msgstr "Prikaže te strani s pomočjo"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "The drop down list with currency codes and names"
msgstr "Spustni seznam s kodami in imeni valut"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects an other currency to work with"
msgstr "Izbere drugo valuto za delo"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reference currency, rates origin"
msgstr "Referenčna valuta, izvor tečajev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines from where &keurocalc; should download the exchange "
"rates between the reference currency and other currencies. The following "
"choices are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev določa, od kod &keurocalc; mora prenesti menjalne tečaje med "
"referenčno valuto in drugimi valutami. Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, no network access (fixed rates only)"
msgstr "Evro, brez dostopa do omrežja (samo fiksne cene)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. No variable rate is downloaded or used. The "
"only available currencies are the ones that have a fixed conversion rate "
"with the euro."
msgstr ""
"Evro je referenčna valuta. Spremenljiva stopnja se ne prenaša ali uporablja. "
"Edine razpoložljive valute so tiste, ki imajo fiksno menjalno razmerje z "
"evrom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid "This setting is adapted to computers with no network access."
msgstr "Ta nastavitev je prilagojena računalnikom brez dostopa do omrežja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, European Central Bank"
msgstr "Evro, Evropska centralna banka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. The fixed exchange rates are available. "
"&keurocalc; attempts to download the variable rates from the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/eurofxref/\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Evro je referenčna valuta. Na voljo so fiksni menjalni tečaji. &keurocalc; "
"poskuša prenesti spremenljive obrestne mere iz <ulink url=\"http://www.ecb."
"int/stats/eurofxref/\">Evropske centralne banke (ECB)</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, Time Genie"
msgstr "Evro, Time Genie"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. The fixed exchange rates are available. "
"&keurocalc; attempts to download the variable rates from the <ulink url="
"\"http://rss.timegenie.com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie (TG)</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Evro je referenčna valuta. Na voljo so fiksni menjalni tečaji. &keurocalc; "
"poskuša prenesti spremenljive tečaje iz <ulink url=\"http://rss.timegenie."
"com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie (TG)</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default currency"
msgstr "Privzeta valuta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the other currency that is used when &keurocalc; starts "
"up or when the user validates the new settings."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev določa drugo valuto, ki se uporablja, ko &keurocalc; zažene "
"ali ko uporabnik potrdi nove nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that the selected currency might not be provided by the selected "
"rates source. In that case, the first available currency in the list is used."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da izbrani vir tečajev morda ne zagotavlja izbrane valute. V "
"tem primeru se uporabi prva razpoložljiva valuta na seznamu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rounding"
msgstr "Zaokroževanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines how the results should be presented in the display "
"area. Internally, all computations are done with the precision offered by "
"the mathematical library, but it usually makes no sense presenting tenths of "
"cents. The following rounding methods are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev določa, kako naj bodo rezultati predstavljeni v območju "
"prikaza. Interno se vsi izračuni izvajajo z natančnostjo, ki jo ponuja "
"matematična knjižnica, vendar običajno ni smiselno predstavljati desetink "
"centov. Na voljo so naslednji načini zaokroževanja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Official rounding rules"
msgstr "Uradna pravila zaokroževanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The EU conversion rules or other official conversion rules are used. It "
"means that the result is rounded to the next unit for currencies like the "
"Japanese yen or the Italian lira, and rounded to the next hundredth of unit "
"(<quote>cents</quote>) for currencies like the euro or the dollar."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljajo se pravila EU za pretvorbo ali druga uradna pravila za "
"pretvorbo. To pomeni, da je rezultat zaokrožen na naslednjo enoto za valute, "
"kot sta japonski jen ali italijanska lira, in zaokrožen na naslednjo "
"stotinko enote (<quote>centov</quote>) za valute, kot sta evro ali dolar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, 158.323 yen would be rounded to 158 yen. 12.537 euro would be "
"rounded to 12.54 euro."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, 158,323 jena bi bilo zaokroženo na 158 jenov. 12,537 evra bi "
"zaokrožili na 12,54 evra."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smallest coin method"
msgstr "Metoda najmanjšega kovanca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result is rounded to the next value of the smallest coin that circulates "
"in the country that uses that currency. For disappeared currencies like the "
"Italian lira, it uses the smallest coin that used to circulate before the "
"currency has been withdrawn: in the case of the Italian lira, it was the 50 "
"liras coin."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat se zaokroži na naslednjo vrednost najmanjšega kovanca, ki je v "
"obtoku v državi, ki uporablja to valuto. Za izginule valute, kot je "
"italijanska lira, uporablja najmanjši kovanec, ki je bil v obtoku, preden je "
"bila valuta umaknjena: v primeru italijanske lire je bil to kovanec za 50 "
"lir."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, 1235.9 Italian liras would be rounded to 1250 liras. 39.45 "
"Norwegian crowns would be rounded to 39.50 crowns."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, 1235,9 italijanskih lir bi bilo zaokroženo na 1250 lir. 39,45 "
"norveških kron bi zaokrožili na 39,50 kron."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We lack information about the smallest coins that exist in every country. "
"Please send a bug report if &keurocalc; uses an incorrect value for the "
"smallest available coin in your country, and we will enter that information."
msgstr ""
"Manjka nam informacij o najmanjših kovancih, ki obstajajo v vsaki državi. "
"Pošljite poročilo o napaki, če &keurocalc; uporablja nepravilno vrednost za "
"najmanjši razpoložljivi kovanec v vaši državi, mi pa bomo vnesli to "
"informacijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "No rounding at all"
msgstr "Brez zaokroževanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "The computed value is displayed unchanged, as a floating point number."
msgstr ""
"Izračunana vrednost je prikazana nespremenjena kot število s plavajočo "
"vejico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look and feel"
msgstr "Videz in obnašanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the appearance and behavior of &keurocalc;. The "
"following options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev določa videz in obnašanje &keurocalc;. Na voljo so naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display color"
msgstr "Barva zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The background color of the display areas (both input and result). To change "
"the background color, click on <guibutton>Change...</guibutton>. This opens "
"the standard &kde; color selection dialog. Choose a new color, then press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to validate the new choice."
msgstr ""
"Barva ozadja območij prikaza (tako vnos kot rezultat). Če želite spremeniti "
"barvo ozadja, kliknite <guibutton>Spremeni...</guibutton>. To odpre "
"standardni &kde; pogovorno okno za izbiro barv. Izberite novo barvo in "
"pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da potrdite novo izbiro."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable splash screen"
msgstr "Omogoči začetni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck this box if you do not want to initial picture to appear when "
"&keurocalc; starts."
msgstr ""
"Počistite to polje, če ne želite, da se prikaže začetna slika, ko se "
"&keurocalc; začne."

